item.title: GCP Exam
item.description: Provisonally passed, thought i hadn’t learnt enough before hand, but the 3 days training at the google academy followed by 2 days the following week seemed to be enough to get through I haven’t done a exam for a long time so although im not convinced I Will spend a lot of time on GCP at work it was a interesting training course and I Will use it at some point
